ai_prompt_template:
You are an expert clinical analyst reviewing patient lab results.

Based on these similar past analyses by experts:
{examples}

Now analyze this new patient record:
{record}

Respond with ONLY a JSON object in this exact format (no markdown, no extra text):
{{
  "summary": "Brief 1-2 sentence summary of key findings",
  "analysis": "Detailed analysis paragraph explaining the clinical significance",
  "risk_assessment": "low|moderate|high|critical",
  "patterns": [
    {{"type": "pattern_type", "field": "field_name", "description": "what was found"}}
  ],
  "recommended_actions": ["action 1", "action 2"],
  "additional_tests": ["test 1", "test 2"]
}}

Pattern types: abnormal_value, correlation, risk_indicator, trend, normal
Risk levels: low, moderate, high, critical
